What is Church Events Calendar?

ChurchEvents is a calendar extra for MODx Revolution was initially designed specifically for churches
 but would be useful in many other contexts.  Churchevents now supports templates and translations.

Requirements
    FormIt

History

ChurchEvents was written by Josh Gulledge to be a complete calendar for MODX Revolution, 
first release was in early 2011.  In November 2011, ChurchEvents was rewretten to 
meet MODX coding standards.


Database Tables:
church_calendar, church_ecategory, church_events, church_location_permissions, church_location_type, church_locations

